{"tid":2327531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北韓據報買俄羅斯疫苗  金正恩料不會接種","createTime":"2020-12-16T06:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T09:07:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6fe80f1c360ea3e5ecd4362a5af27fb13df9b655","tid":2327531,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"新冠疫情全球大流行，多間藥廠研發新冠肺炎疫苗，北韓一直聲稱「零確診」，但似乎仍與爆疫國家般渴求新冠疫苗。據早前有媒體報道指，中國已向北韓領袖金正恩及其家人提供新冠疫苗。日本媒體周二報道指，北韓已購買俄羅斯的新冠疫苗，北韓高官已開始接種。<br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》引述消息人士指，北韓已從俄羅斯購買疫苗，相信該款疫苗為「史普尼克5號」（Sputnik V）。<br />\n<br />\n《朝日新聞》報道指，暫未知道北韓的購買規模。對於金正恩會否接種該款疫苗，消息人士則指，在安全性尚未確認的階段，估計金正恩不會接種。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯官方早前指出，「史普尼克5號」的效用率高達96%，而且餘下4%人士縱染上新冠肺炎，也會只有輕微的流鼻涕、咳嗽及發燒，肺部卻沒有受損。不過，普京至今尚未接種俄羅斯新冠疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket .com/article/2830009</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f7310e27db9b49432c8d006b71d14c6e5819f496","tid":2327531,"uid":7323,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">聰明的金正恩，你地個個打曬。我仲使咩打。</span>"},{"pid":"b9ac7ecc2494525fad056429afe7ce8c2fae0a06","tid":2327531,"uid":70786,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:32:47.000Z","msg":"防疫專家我只信金正恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d8a290c77beaad7ffaa5c0f41230ec8b5dce22","tid":2327531,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"之前話金仔打強國野睇來係假新聞來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3755fca882050d4b64880d7559aac726510aa6af","tid":2327531,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f7310e27db9b49432c8d006b71d14c6e5819f496","tid":2327531,"uid":7323,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">聰明的金正恩，你地個個打曬。我仲使咩打。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341b32986a02c9a474d0cd31a3b0567c8b8f8403","tid":2327531,"uid":275692,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:42:10.000Z","msg":"確診北韓市民獲接種子彈"},{"pid":"a7454980ae0f64cba9875914f8862562c1f303fd","tid":2327531,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"幾時都話金仔醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc441d99f769959394cf796e3939dd9d3170feb","tid":2327531,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"北韓有無醫生可以獨立兼有足夠醫學知識評估都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7af26b851e21b8334d882545154558e1661e36","tid":2327531,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"金仔為何不買芝麻武肺疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eae48b7786e06f19c318a97286dec22d2ea955f","tid":2327531,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"全民試藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cea5370f67ead26636d69fcabcdf7d9d8ff4d9","tid":2327531,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4bc441d99f769959394cf796e3939dd9d3170feb","tid":2327531,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"北韓有無醫生可以獨立兼有足夠醫學知識評估都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:07:03.000Z","msg":"叻嗰啲都送曬去俄羅斯受訓啦"}]}